University Library


About


Contact Us






Contact Us
Our librarians can help you find articles for research papers, cite resources, connect to the library from off campus and more.






            Cross references
          Heading link



 
Copy link



You can contact the UIC University Library in several ways.

For reference or circulation, see our various UIC Library locations.
See our Help Center for answers to many frequently asked questions.






            Link tiles.
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            Email us
                    

                Submit a question or comment, and a UIC Librarian will get back to you with answers.
            









                            Schedule research help
                    

                Make an appointment to meet with a UIC Librarian for research help in-person, online, or over the phone.
            









                            Request course instruction
                    

                Request a Library instruction session for your students.
            









                            Computers and technology help
                    

                Report trouble with printers, computers or access.
            









                            Library website help
                    

                Get help with the UIC Library website and online tools.
            









                            Library directory
                    

                Contact specific Library faculty and staff directly.
            









                            Recommend an item for the Library to Purchase
                    

                Recommend books and other items for the UIC Library to add to its collections.
            










